{"tid":1039271,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"子瑜輸了！娜璉穿超緊身小背心　雪白嫩乳衝出領口…驚呆粉","createTime":"2019-02-27T09:56:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-01T15:16:30.000Z","uid":74065,"like":47,"dislike":841,"uniUserReply":77,"replies":[{"pid":"4cdfd62d7ddb771cdba54c38d6029e1ae1620759","tid":1039271,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T09:56:15.000Z","msg":"南韓超人氣女團TWICE出道4年，享有超高人氣，每次回歸都擁有驚人的成績，不過雖然她們是走青春甜美風，裡面還是有幾個成員的身材可說是非常凹凸有致，除了大家都知道擁有魔鬼身材的隊長志效外，今（26日）天，娜璉曬出美照，穿上白緊身背心的她，雄偉的雙峰呼之欲出，讓粉絲們紛紛大驚，<span style=\"color: red;\">原來她也是「隱乳系」的一員。</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2019/02/26/1799813-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2019%2F02%2F26%2F1799813-XXL.jpg&h=6b2620ff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n▼▲娜璉大曬美照，意外曝光姣好身材。（圖／翻攝自TWICE IG）<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2019/02/26/1799819-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2019%2F02%2F26%2F1799819-XXL.jpg&h=8111c89e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n今天中午，娜璉在TWICE官方IG上曬出一組美照，照片中，她梳著一頭高馬尾，身上穿著白色緊身背心搭配寶藍色外搭，看起來十分青春有活力，不過因為緊身背心的緣故，讓她飽滿的雪乳幾乎要衝出領口，而另一張，她往前傾的照片，雪乳的深溝更是直逼鎖骨，讓網友們忍不住直盯胸看。<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2019/02/26/1799817-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2019%2F02%2F26%2F1799817-XXL.jpg&h=68201b80&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Phs7EmD.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPhs7EmD.gif&h=657a9ca5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"70e0d53bb54c3c134ee6cf0456a58fe262d955ef","tid":1039271,"uid":223790,"like":69,"dislike":6,"score":63,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T09:56:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e6471c4baf033796c131e5a850ad0444aeaebc52","tid":1039271,"uid":223790,"like":16,"dislike":3,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"re